    <item>
      <title>比特币创下 95,000 美元新高，加密货币寻求与特朗普直接沟通</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/bitcoin-btc-on-verge-of-95-000-as-crypto-seeks-direct-line-to-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着数字资产行业推动在白宫设立一个专门负责加密货币政策的新职位，以巩固其对唐纳德·特朗普的影响力，比特币首次突破 95,000 美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/bitcoin-btc-on-verge-of-95-000-as-crypto-seeks-direct-line-to-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 00:50:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Byju 创始人被指控试图利用隐藏现金重获公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/byju-accused-of-trying-to-use-missing-loan-cash-to-buy-back-firm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一份新的法庭文件显示，破产的印度科技公司 Byju’s 的创始人试图利用他向美国贷方隐瞒的贷款收益秘密回购一家被美国受托人接管的软件公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/byju-accused-of-trying-to-use-missing-loan-cash-to-buy-back-firm</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 00:43:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黑石集团向 Lancium AI 建设投资 5 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/blackstone-invests-500-million-in-lancium-ai-buildout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，黑石公司向 Lancium 公司投资逾 5 亿美元，后者正在西德克萨斯州建设超过 5 千兆瓦的数据中心，以满足人工智能应用日益增长的能源需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/blackstone-invests-500-million-in-lancium-ai-buildout</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 00:35:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>百度业绩凸显其人工智能挑战，多头回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/baidu-bulls-retreat-as-earnings-to-spotlight-firm-s-ai-challenge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在百度公司第三季度业绩公布前，投资者对该公司美国上市股票的乐观情绪正在减弱，因为交易员们正在争论这家搜索引擎的人工智能努力是否会带来回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/baidu-bulls-retreat-as-earnings-to-spotlight-firm-s-ai-challenge</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 00:28:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Beyond Doubts 计划以 4000 万美元入股 The Container Store</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/beyond-doubts-planned-40-million-stake-in-the-container-store</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据周三发布的一份声明称，Beyond Inc. 对 The Container Store Group Inc. 是否有能力满足完成对该公司 4000 万美元投资所需的某些新融资要求感到担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/beyond-doubts-planned-40-million-stake-in-the-container-store</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 00:06:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>库存增加后交易商权衡乌克兰风险 油价持稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-21</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国原油库存连续第三周增加后，市场关注乌克兰和中东局势的发展，油价因此趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-21</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 23:32:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
