      <title>亿万富翁高塔姆·阿达尼因涉嫌行贿 2.5 亿美元遭美国指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-20/gautam-adani-charged-by-us-over-alleged-250m-bribe-plot-video</link>
